QuestData.Title: Spare Parts Up In Here!
QuestData.Description: Whew, that was tough. I didn't think we'd make it, $n. We better get these parts back to Chief Blastgineer Bombgutz. I think I hear the gnome flying machines buzzing outside. We haven't got a minute to lose!
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Crate of Spare Parts to Chief Blastgineer Bombgutz at Krom'gar Fortress in Stonetalon Mountains.
